            "title": "PROMISING TRUST AND AUTHENTICITY",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>The purity, potency and quality of each drop are tried, tested and true. The liquid gold within each jar can be traced all the way back to its origin – right down to the honey hunters who lovingly harvested it.</p><p>Independently certified, authenticated and proven, <a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">Medicinal Mad Honey</a> is imbued with the pristine purity of native Nepal. From the Himalayan hive, into the jar, and into your home.</p>",
